News.Title: Rockingdeals Circular Announces National and Global Expansion with Quick Commerce Focus
News.Summary: Rockingdeals Circular has announced plans to expand its operations both nationally and globally, with a strategic focus on quick commerce services.

News.Title: Rockingdeals Reports Strong Q3 FY25 Results and Sets Ambitious Revenue Target
News.Summary: Rockingdeals has reported robust financial results for Q3 FY25, with revenue matching the figures from the first half of the year. The company maintained a consistent 15% profit after tax (PAT) margin. Looking ahead, Rockingdeals has set an ambitious target of achieving 400-500 crore revenue by FY27. The company currently has a market capitalization of 324 crore.

News.Title: Rockingdeals Circular Projects Significant Revenue Growth and Profitability
News.Summary: Rockingdeals Circular has announced expectations of achieving revenue between 400-500 crore rupees by fiscal year 2027, following a strategic investment. The company also projects profit after tax (PAT) margins of 10-15% for the same period.

News.Title: RockingDeals Circular Economy Signs Agreement with FabIndia
News.Summary: RockingDeals Circular Economy has entered into a sales or return agreement with FabIndia. The agreement allows FabIndia to utilize space within RockingDeals' stores.
